This paper deals with the problem of detecting game bots in MMORPGs, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed method involves using financial analysis and LSTM, which are both techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of data mining algorithms to analyze behavioral and social actions of characters, which falls under the category of social computing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves the use of algorithms to analyze time-series data, which is a common problem in data science (cs.DS).
